      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/07/the-whole-point/#comment-13625"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-03-01T02:42:11-05:00">Monday, March 1, 2010 at 2:42 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks, BaydraOtis!  These photos are all Polaroids &#8211; real ones, not digital approximations &#8211; that I scan and upload.  I do use PhotoShop to edit out dust and the like, but otherwise, this is what they look like!  Polaroid film is terrific.</p>
    </div>

