    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, Everyone:</p>
<p>I just made this salsa verde and put it on boiled red potatoes (split in two) and green beans that I got at the farmer&#39;s market.  I brought it to a picnic where we ate on a quilt and listened to a band.  It was perfect on all levels!  Great recipe.</p>
    </div>

